284
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:59,590
Market Structure Market structure is when trader analyzes

285
00:10:59,590 --> 00:11:02,450
the behavior, condition, and flow of the market.

286
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:05,890
An uptrend structure is characterized by price forming

287
00:11:05,890 --> 00:11:09,210
higher highs and higher lows, while downtrend structure

288
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:12,010
is characterized by price forming lower highs and

289
00:11:12,010 --> 00:11:12,630
