290
00:11:13,690 --> 00:11:16,570
Break of Structure It is when price breaks

291
00:11:16,570 --> 00:11:18,750
the previous price peak during a trend.

292
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:21,310
For example, if the price forms a higher

293
00:11:21,310 --> 00:11:23,530
highs and higher lows, this break of the

294
00:11:23,530 --> 00:11:25,430
previous highs is called break of structure.

295
00:11:26,430 --> 00:11:29,690
Change of Character It occurs when price breaks

296
00:11:29,690 --> 00:11:32,470
the previous structure during a trend, often signaling

297
00:11:32,470 --> 00:11:34,450
a reversal from that current trend.

298
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:37,030
For example, if the price is forming higher

299
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:39,170
highs and higher lows, then it breaks the

300
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:41,870
previous lows forming lower lows, this is called

301
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:42,850
a change of character.

